{"tid":2151671,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"特朗普：原本同習近平有良好關係    已有一段時間未與習近平通話","createTime":"2020-08-11T13:32:39.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-11T14:51:01.000Z","uid":39464,"like":31,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"b895c07607f9040fd2a2ae6c86ea658120517bbe","tid":2151671,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-11T13:32:39.000Z","msg":"特朗普接受電台節目訪問時表示，原本同習近平有良好關係，但在新型肺炎疫情後感覺不再一樣。特朗普形容，疫情爆發較貿易爭議更惡劣，疫情引致死亡，世界停頓，他形容是一種恥辱。<br />\n<br />\n美國多次指責中國未有及時向外公布新型肺炎疫情，中國亦多次反駁，已經如實及時向外公布，美國的指責並沒有理據。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1543168-20200811.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1543168-20200811.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=9ox5Qr7lvCKhSYdyRcf9Fmmu51%2BDyw7Majob2ybULac%3D&h=f0657de0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1543168-20200811.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=92993ee8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1543168-20200811.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"07d7069d8e14ebe0056fbb89530f18fe5d8790ee","tid":2151671,"uid":39464,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-11T13:33:12.000Z","msg":"Trump says 'great' bond with China's Xi changed after COVID-19<br />\n<br />\nU.S. President Donald Trump on Tuesday said his relationship with Chinese President Xi Jinping has frayed in the wake of the novel coronavirus pandemic and that he has not spoken to his Chinese counterpart in a long time.<br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;I used to have a very good relationship with him,&rdquo; Trump told Fox Sports Radio in an interview, citing their Phase One trade deal last year. &ldquo;I had a great relationship with President Xi. I like him, but I don&rsquo;t feel the same way now.&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\nTrump said his feelings changed amid COVID-19.<br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;I certainly feel differently. I had a very, very good relationship, and I haven&rsquo;t spoken to him in a long time.&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\nTrump, who is seeking re-election in the Nov. 3 U.S. election, made challenging China a key part of his 2016 presidential campaign and touted his friendly ties with Xi during much of his first term in office as he sought to make good on his trade deal promises.<br />\n<br />\nBut he said on Tuesday that the fallout from the outbreak was worse than the conflict over trade. &ldquo;This is a thousand times the trade deal what happened with all of the death and ... the world had to shutdown. It&rsquo;s a disgrace,&rdquo; he told Fox.<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://ca.reuters.com/article/topNews/idCAKCN2571QM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fca.reuters.com%2Farticle%2FtopNews%2FidCAKCN2571QM&d=9ox5Qr7lvCKhSYdyRcf9Fmmu51%2BDyw7Majob2ybULac%3D&h=f12faeb8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fca.reuters.com%2Farticle%2FtopNews%2FidCAKCN2571QM&h=4ed0bf17\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://ca.reuters.com/article/topNews/idCAKCN2571QM</a>"},{"pid":"6686fe2cea31842a0ece2ba60d7f62ada6b48bfe","tid":2151671,"uid":283912,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-11T13:34:23.000Z","msg":"借個位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n[有圖] 陳敏之呢對屌西腳真係可以奶成晚<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2151673\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2151673</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"212eff8aaa9360119ce4d4e7384315fe00ac2081","tid":2151671,"uid":169530,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-11T13:34:26.000Z","msg":"要絕交了<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />？"},{"pid":"67d6d9b04f3d1e1962e5e6d38d8d64e6c4f28bfe","tid":2151671,"uid":63934,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-11T13:34:52.000Z","msg":"即係冷戰<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_shocking.g